OL,3,CThousands raised in memory of five-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl who died after car crash
OL,6,FMore than seven thousand pounds has
OL,7,Fbeen raised in memory of a five-year-
OL,8,Fold girl who died after a car crash in
OL,9,FLancashire.
OL,11,FAlana Moscrop died in hospital last
OL,12,Fweek after the collision in Gisburn. A
OL,13,F60-year-old woman and a five-year-old
OL,14,Fboy remain in hospital.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Alana's family said:
OL,18,F"On Tuesday afternoon our lives were
OL,19,Fchanged forever. We lost our
OL,20,Fbeautiful, fun, perfect little
OL,21,Fprincess.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780229466
OL,3,CThousands raised in memory of five-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl who died after car crash
OL,6,F"She will forever be missed but never
OL,7,Fforgotten by mum, Natalie, dad,
OL,8,FAndrew, twin brother Finn and everyone
OL,9,Fwho was lucky enough to meet her.
OL,11,F"We are beyond broken-hearted without
OL,12,Fher, she was our loving bundle of
OL,13,Fenergy and joy."
OL,15,FThe fundraising page was setup to help
OL,16,Fthe family pay for her funeral.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
