CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780229466
OL,3,CThousands raised in memory of five-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl who died after car crash
OL,6,FPosting on the page, organiser Tom
OL,7,FSmith said: "The loss of Alana has
OL,8,Fleft her family facing unimaginable
OL,9,Fheartbreak. As they try to come to
OL,10,Fterms with this devastating loss, we
OL,11,Fwould like to help ease the financial
OL,12,Fburden of giving Alana the beautiful
OL,13,Ffarewell she deserves.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780229466
OL,3,CThousands raised in memory of five-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl who died after car crash
OL,6,F"We are raising money to help cover
OL,7,Fthe costs of Alana's funeral and to
OL,8,Fsupport her family during this
OL,9,Fincredibly difficult time. Any
OL,10,Fdonation, no matter how small, would
OL,11,Fmean the world and allow her loved
OL,12,Fones to focus on remembering and
OL,13,Fcelebrating her precious life."
OL,15,FLancashire Police responded to the
OL,16,Fcrash involving a Skoda and VW Golf on
OL,17,Fthe A59 in Gisburn, Lancashire, on
OL,18,FThursday 21 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780229466
OL,3,CThousands raised in memory of five-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl who died after car crash
OL,6,FThe driver of the Volkswagen, a man in
OL,7,Fhis 20s also suffered serious
OL,8,Finjuries, and remains in hospital. He
OL,9,Fis being treated as a witness.
OL,11,FSgt Laura Kendall of our Serious
OL,12,FCollision Investigation Unit said:
OL,13,F"My, and my team's thoughts are very
OL,14,Fmuch with Alana's family, and all
OL,15,Fthose who knew and loved her. It's
OL,16,Fclear from their tribute just how
OL,17,Floved and adored she was, and it is
OL,18,Fdevastating news that she has died.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780229466
OL,3,CThousands raised in memory of five-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl who died after car crash
OL,6,F"They have understandably been asked
OL,7,Ffor privacy at this terrible time, and
OL,8,FI ask that people please respect that.
OL,10,F"Our enquiries into the collision are
OL,11,Fvery much ongoing, and we are
OL,12,Fcontinuing to appeal for anyone with
OL,13,Finformation or footage that could help
OL,14,Fus.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780229466
OL,3,CThousands raised in memory of five-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl who died after car crash
OL,6,F"Whilst we are appealing for
OL,7,Finformation, I also make a request
OL,8,Fthat this is passed on through the
OL,9,Fappropriate channels, and people
OL,10,Frefrain from speculating online or
OL,11,Fotherwise. Please remember that a
OL,12,Flittle girl has lost her life, and a
OL,13,Flittle boy and two adults remain
OL,14,Finjured. This collision has and will
OL,15,Fcontinue to effect real people ` and
OL,16,Fseeing unnecessary speculation online
OL,17,Fwill only make matters more
OL,18,Fdistressing for them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@VO]
